- The integer array parameter `houses` must not be null.
- The integer array parameter `houses` length is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to 100.
- All values in the integer array parameter `houses` are greater than or equal to 1 and are less than or equal to 10000.
- The integer parameter `k` is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to the length of the integer array parameter `houses`.
- The integer result is the minimum total distance between each house and its nearest mailbox.